  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed dormer roof extension, by reason of its size, bulk, design, position, and proportions, would result in an incompatible and obtrusive form of development which would adversely affect the character and appearance of the host dwelling and the conservation area. &amp;nbsp; The proposal is therefore contrary to policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP3 (Designated Heritage Assets of the Hackney Local Plan 2020 and guidance contained in the Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD.&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed rooflights, by reason of its design and position would result in an visual clutter which would adversely affect the character and appearance of the host dwelling and the conservation area. &amp;nbsp; The proposal is therefore contrary to policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP3 (Designated Heritage Assets)&amp;nbsp;of the Hackney Local Plan 2020 and guidance contained in the Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD.&lt;/p&gt;"
